Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話  一起刷牆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  下島  你為甚麼那麼賣力啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我以前參加過學生運動  總覺得這種青春的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是聽我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  右邊  右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊？  右？  這樣行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  反方向啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過頭了過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就像學園祭一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭復活簽名裁決日
